Redirects:
'/site/%web_locale%' => 'siteRedirect',  => Redirects to the homepage of the contact
'/cat/[:idcat]/%web_locale%' => 'categoryRedirect',
'/content/[:idcontent]/%web_locale%' => 'contentRedirect',
'/brand/[:idbrand]/%web_locale%' => 'brandRedirect',
'/search/%web_locale%' => 'searchRedirect',
'/product/[:root]/%web_locale%' => 'productRedirect', 

Examples:
siteRedirect     => https://redirect.bicgraphic.eu/site/%web_locale%  
categoryRedirect => https://redirect.bicgraphic.eu/web/cat/101144/%web_locale%  
contentRedirect  => https://redirect.bicgraphic.eu/web/content/100400/%web_locale%
productRedirect  => https://redirect.bicgraphic.eu/web/product/3460053062/%web_locale%